Yong AOA/AOB Diversity

Dylan Bodington

2023-02-08

ps_AOA <- readRDS("./AOA/ps_AOA.Rds")
ps_AOA_alves <- readRDS("./AOA/ps_AOA_alves.Rds")
ps_AOB <- readRDS("./AOB/ps_AOB.Rds")
ps_COM <- readRDS("./COM/ps_COM.Rds")
alpha_AOA_plot <- plot_richness(
  ps_AOA,
  x = 'rep',
  color = 'sip',
  measures = c(
    'Chao1', 'Shannon', 'Simpson', 'Fisher'
    ),
  nrow = 2
  ) +
  labs(
    title = "Diversity of AOA",
    color = "SIP",
    x = "Sample",
  ) +
  scale_color_npg()
alpha_AOA_plot

alpha_AOA_box_plot <- boxplot_alpha(
  ps_AOA,
  x_var = "name",
  index = "shannon"
  ) +
  labs(
    title = "Diversity of AOA (Shannon)",
    fill = "Sample",
    x = "Sample",
    y = "Shannon Diversity Index"
  ) +
  theme(
    legend.position = "none",
  ) +
  scale_fill_npg()
alpha_AOA_box_plot

ps <- tax_glom(ps_AOA, taxrank = "Phylum", bad_empty = "Bacteria_unidentified") %>%
  merge_samples2("name", funs = list()) %>%
  transform_sample_counts(function(x) x / sum(x))

taxa_AOA_plot <- plot_bar(aggregate_rare(ps, "Phylum", detection = 0.001, prevalence = 0.001), fill="Phylum") +
  labs(
    title = "AOA Community Composition",
    fill = "Cluster",
    x = "Sample",
    y = "Relative Abundance"
  ) +
  theme(
    axis.text.x = element_text(
      angle = -30,
      face = "italic"
    )
  ) +
  scale_fill_npg()
taxa_AOA_plot

ps <- tax_glom(ps_AOA, taxrank = "Phylum", bad_empty = "Bacteria_unidentified") %>%
    merge_samples2("rep", funs = list()) %>%
  transform_sample_counts(function(x) x / sum(x))

taxa_AOA_rep_plot <- plot_bar(aggregate_rare(ps, "Phylum", detection = 0.01, prevalence = 0.01), fill="Phylum") +
  labs(
    title = "AOA Community Composition (All Replicates)",
    fill = "Cluster",
    x = "Replicates",
    y = "Relative Abundance"
  ) +
  theme(
    axis.text.x = element_text(
      angle = -30,
      face = "italic"
    )
  ) +
  scale_fill_npg()

taxa_AOA_rep_plot
